sentences: Emi Takei (武井 咲, Takei Emi, born December 25, 1993) is a Japanese actress and model.
Aspiring to become a model, she declared to her parents on her entry to junior high school that she would become a model within three years.
In 2006, she entered the 11th Japan Bishōjo Contest and won in not only one, but two categories: she received the Model Division Award and the Multi-Media Award.
